entries.description:
This song doesn't belong to me all credit goes to real artist

orinal song - https://youtu.be/0FsK_xosi9g

This song is old but it is nice .This song wrote by sabin rai, thank you sabin rai for this lovely song

#sabinrai #lyrics 

lyrics

MA SANSAR JITNE - SABIN RAI

ma sansar jitne aat gardai chhu
matrai timi mero saath basi deu
bhawisya le gaune geet ma rachdai chhu
matra timi  sur ma taal milai deu
yahi ho aartha rachnuko
itihasma amar rahos
timro ra mero kahani sadhai sadhai


jaba hidhda hidhdai thakchhu ma kahile kahi
teti bela mer aad bani deu
jindagiko mod ma sochna sakina bhane
timro mithjo bichar malai deu
yahi ho aartha bhannu ko
sapana thulo chaina
bilauna garna naparos...jindagima...


sunaulo hamro bhawisya
sakar hunchha malai bharosa chha
ma harpal timro rakschhya  garne chhu
matrai timi aatma bal bani deu
bhawisya le gaune geet ma rachdai chu
matrai timi sur ma taal milai deu
yahi ho aartha rachnu ko
itihas  ma  amar rahos
timro ra mero kahani...sadhai...sadhai..

entries.description:
#TuborgOpenSessions #OpenForFun
 
Tuborg proudly announces Tuborg Open Sessions, a YouTube series featuring live studio-recorded performances by various artists, established and emerging. From old classics to current fan favorites to up and coming talents, the digital platform will welcome to share their creativity, collaborate with each other and experiment and mix various genres.

Tuborg has a long and proud heritage with music, helping introduce new genres and artists to new markets. With Tuborg Open Sessions, the brand is hoping to set new trends in terms of musical collaboration in Nepal by breathing new life to old classics and paving a path for upcoming artists.

With Channel Arbitrary, one of the top YouTube channels in Nepal for music (creator), Tuborg Open Sessions intends to fulfill what’s lacking in Nepalese music industry currently; a complete digital platform for artists and musicians to experiment, work together and gain new experiences and sharing them with others to see where it takes them, therefore, also creating opportunities for new artists. The series will have Nepali and other instruments to cater different artists and their musical genres.

Music conducted and rearranged by Manoj Kumar KC
Vocal/ Acoustic Guitar: Ishan Raj Onta
Guitar/ Backing Vocal: Raunaq Singh Adhikari

entries.description:
Mooskaan is a song that I wrote forever ago, around 2010. You all asked for the song and here it is, finally. A new song of an old song.

Thank you to everyone who has shown such tremendous support. Your support drives me to write more songs and make more music. Thank you for asking for this song.

Thank you to Sumit for being such an integral part of this song.

Official release for Sajjan Raj Vaidya's 'Mooskaan'.

Written | Produced | Composed by: Sajjan Raj Vaidya
Flute by Sumit Maharjan

Subscribe to Sajjan's channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/SajjanRajVaidya
Watch all of Sajjan's videos here: https://www.youtube.com/user/sajjanrajvaidya/videos

Visit our website: https://www.SajjanRajVaidya.com

Follow Sumit on:
Instagram: @timusic_mhj

Follow Sajjan on:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/sajjanrajvaidya
Instagram: @SajjanRajVaidya
Twitter: @sajjanrajvaidya
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/sajjanrajvaidya

Lyrics: 
Timilai thaha chaina, timro mooskaan le,
Malai ke garcha, timro mooskaan le.
Timilai thaha chaina, herda timile herda malai,
Ke huncha, Ke huncha, timi aundaa, mooskuraunda malai.

Timro naam, timro aawaaj, timro nyano nyano sparsha,
Mero haath, mero paila, sabaile timilai khojcha.
Timilai thaha chaina, tara maya dherai dherai garchu,
Matra timi haansideu.

Timi aau pharkera, pharkera yeta,
Timilai naheree, sakena basera yahan;
Timi nahundaa, malai gahro aphthyaro huncha,
Tyesaile, ahile nai aau, mooskuraau, satau malai.

Timro naam, timro aawaaj, timro nyano nyano sparsha,
Mero hath, mero paila sabaile timilai khojcha.
Timilai thaha chaina, tara maya dherai dherai garchu,
Matra timi haansideu.

Timro antrikshya maa, laijau na malai pani,
Timro chaanyaan maa baschu timrai chandrama bani,
Aakashai bharine gari maya timilai ma garaunlaa maya,
Matra timi haansideu.
